    <Ritual>
        <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
            <ab>YR2.2 (mss. 360, 370):</ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                <em>aɱiia zaōϑre barəsmanaēca ahurəm mazdąm</em> gāh ī rapihwin abāyēd guftan -:- māhiiaēibiiō ēč gyāg abāyēd guftan rōz ud māh guftan</ab>  
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                "(After) <em>aɱiia zaōϑre barəsmanaēca ahurəm mazdąm</em> he must say the <em>gāh</em> of <em>rapihwin</em>. (Then), he must not say (the section) <em>māhiiaēibiiō</em>. 
                (He should continue with the recitation of) the day and the month."</ab>
        </Nerangs>
    </Ritual>
